  "summary": "neural-network-scan exfiltrates host information to attacker-controlled C2",
  "details": "The package ships collect.js, which collects host identifiers (os.hostname(), os.homedir()) and filesystem state via fs.existsSync probes, then POSTs the data to the hardcoded endpoint http://aab.sportsontheweb.net. The script imports child_process, http, https, fs, and os — the canonical sysinfo/exfil shape — and the destination is hardcoded into the file body, not a configurable parameter. Installing or loading this package leaks installer host metadata to an attacker-controlled domain.",
